01:04:18,480 --> 01:04:21,640
"I salute people who have courage."

848
01:04:21,800 --> 01:04:25,320
"Courage helps you to continue
to live your day-to-day life."

849
01:04:26,200 --> 01:04:30,480
"Courage is something...
