at the present scale.

949
01:11:39,560 --> 01:11:41,960
So the answer is powering down.

950
01:11:42,400 --> 01:11:47,400
Right now, hundreds of communities
are starting to take these steps.

951
01:11:47,560 --> 01:11:50,760
