shoot up or if there's scarcity,

955
01:12:04,960 --> 01:12:07,960
they may find
the supermarket shelves empty.

956
01:12:08,120 --> 01:12:11,040
That they won't
be able to heat their homes,

957
01:12:11,200 --> 01:12:13,000
that they won't be able to travel.

958
01:12:16,160 --> 01:12:19,960
We must talk about how to control

959
01:12:21,560 --> 01:12:23,560
our cheap desire.

960
01:12:25,200 --> 01:12:27,720
I think something
we can all do worldwide

961
