in a state of emergency.

965
01:12:47,080 --> 01:12:49,560
We delude ourselves into thinking

966
01:12:49,720 --> 01:12:52,040
that these problems are the creation

967
01:12:52,200 --> 01:12:55,240
of our nation, government,
religion or race,

968
01:12:55,400 --> 01:12:57,400
but this is not so.

969
01:12:58,160 --> 01:12:59,840
The problem lies within

970
01:13:00,000 --> 01:13:02,480
each individual's consciousness.

971
01:13:04,320 --> 01:13:07,640
I don't believe in humankind.
